trans-unit.source: Provides functionality for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)] models.
trans-unit.target: Gir funksjonalitet for [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_3d](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-3d-md.md)] modeller.

trans-unit.source: Objects of this type include <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeometryModel3D>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Light>, and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3DGroup>.
trans-unit.target: Objekter av denne typen inkluderer <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeometryModel3D>, <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Light>, og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3DGroup>.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3DGroup> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Light> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.GeometryModel3D>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D> class to render Model3D objects.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D>klassen for å gjengi Model3D objekter.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D>

trans-unit.source: You can compose Model3D objects by using a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3DGroup> to form a single model.
trans-unit.target: Du kan lage Model3D objekter ved hjelp av en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3DGroup>å utgjøre et enkelt modellen.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3DGroup>

trans-unit.source: You can share Model3D objects among <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D> objects to make multiple instances in a scene.
trans-unit.target: Du kan dele Model3D objekter blant <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D>skal være flere forekomster i et bilde.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ModelVisual3D>

trans-unit.source: Gets a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D"></xref> that specifies the axis-aligned bounding box of this <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter en <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D"> </xref> som angir akse justert avgrensende boksen for dette <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D"></xref> bounding box for the model.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Rect3D"> </xref> ramme for modellen.

trans-unit.source: Creates a modifiable clone of this <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D"></xref>, and makes deep copies of this object's values.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en kan endres kopi av denne <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D"> </xref>, og gjør dype kopier av verdier for dette objektet.

trans-unit.source: When copying dependency properties, this method copies resource references and data bindings (although they might no longer resolve) but does not copy animations or their current values.
trans-unit.target: Når du kopierer avhengighetsegenskaper, denne metoden kopierer ressursen referanser og data bindinger (selv om de ikke kan løse), men ikke kopiere animasjoner eller gjeldende verdier.

trans-unit.source: This method is used to produce modifiable copies of frozen <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> objects or of any <xref:System.Windows.Freezable> object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden brukes til å kunne endres kopiere låste <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>objekter eller noen <xref:System.Windows.Freezable>objektet.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable> </xref:System.Windows.Freezable>

trans-unit.source: For convenience, this method shadows the inherited version with a strongly typed implementation.
trans-unit.target: Når som helst skygger denne metoden arvede versjon med en forespørselsparameter av sterk type implementering.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.Clone%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.Clone%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable.Clone%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A modifiable clone of the current object.
trans-unit.target: En kan endres kopi av det gjeldende objektet.

trans-unit.source: The cloned object's <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen*> property will be <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> even if the source's <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen*> property was <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Det klonede objektet <> </> *> blir <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> selv om kildens <> </> *> egenskapen var <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Creates a modifiable clone of this <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D"></xref> object, and makes deep copies of this object's current values.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en kan endres kopi av denne <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Model3D"> </xref> objekt, og gjør dype kopier av gjeldende verdier for dette objektet.

trans-unit.source: Resource references, data bindings, and animations are not copied; however, their current values are copied.
trans-unit.target: Refererer til ressursen, databindinger og animasjoner kopieres ikke; imidlertid kopieres gjeldende verdier.

trans-unit.source: For convenience, this method shadows the inherited version with a strongly typed implementation.
trans-unit.target: Når som helst skygger denne metoden arvede versjon med en forespørselsparameter av sterk type implementering.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.CloneCurrentValue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.CloneCurrentValue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Freezable.CloneCurrentValue%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A modifiable clone of the current object.
trans-unit.target: En kan endres kopi av det gjeldende objektet.

trans-unit.source: The cloned object's <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen*> property will be <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> even if the source's <xref:System.Windows.Freezable.IsFrozen*> property was <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
